3) Frontend PRD
Product name

Waste Sorting Dashboard

Purpose

Provide a visual interface for monitoring waste detection events, system status, statistics, and device activity in real time.

Goals
Show live video or picturs of waste as well as recent detection results.
Display waste category and confidence.
Visualize sorting activity over time.
Show bin health and device status.
Give an operator a clear view of system performance.
Users
System operator
Research supervisor
Demo audience
Maintenance personnel
Scope
In scope
Live detection feed
Detection history table
Category summary charts
System status indicators
Device connection status
Error and alert display
Out of scope
Training the AI model
Direct hardware control
Firmware flashing
Complex admin workflows
Functional requirements
The dashboard shall display the latest detection result.
The dashboard shall show the waste class, confidence, and timestamp.
The dashboard shall display a live or periodically refreshed event list.
The dashboard shall show analytics such as total detections and category counts.
The dashboard shall show device status, including online/offline state.
The dashboard shall show error messages when backend or device issues occur.
The dashboard shall allow filtering by date, device, or category.
The dashboard shall support image preview for each detection.
The dashboard shall show sorting activity in near real time.
The dashboard shall be responsive on desktop and tablet screens.
Non-functional requirements
Fast page loading.
Clean and simple UI.
Responsive layout.
Easy-to-read charts and tables.
Real-time updates without manual refresh where possible.
