Acceptance criteria
The dashboard displays new detections automatically or on refresh.
Users can see classification results clearly.
Charts and tables update with backend data.
The interface works well on common screen sizes.
Errors and offline states are visible to the user.
Recommended development order
Firmware
Build the sensor-to-camera-to-servo cycle first.
Backend
Add the model inference service and API response flow.
Frontend
Build the dashboard after backend endpoints are stable.
MVP definition

A working MVP should do only this:

Detect presence with ultrasonic
Capture waste image
Send image to backend
Classify into 3 categories
Show result on dashboard
Trigger the correct servo path